headline: Why BigBear.ai Stock Is Skyrocketing Today
summary: BigBear.ai stock is surging Thursday amid a day of bullish momentum for the broader market.  While there haven't been any major new developments for the company, investors are continuing to bet on defense artificial intelligence (AI) stocks.  The company's share price was up 13.6% as of 2 p.m. ET amid a 0.5% jump for the S&P 500 (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) and a 0.7% jump for the Nasdaq Composite (NASDAQINDEX: ^IXIC).

headline: Prediction: This Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stock Will Be Worth $1 Trillion in 5 Years
summary: Palantir has jumped 5x in the past year, and it still has room for more upside despite an expensive valuation.  The rapid adoption of AI software to enable productivity improvements is turning out to be a tailwind for this company.  Palantir is growing at a faster pace than the end market it is serving, which could help it justify its expensive valuation in the long run.

headline: 2 Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stocks the U.S. Government Wants to Support
summary: Fast-growing Palantir is quickly becoming a critical government contractor with an expanding footprint.  You may not even realize how much artificial intelligence (AI) has already infiltrated daily lives -- voice assistants on smartphones, personalized recommendations when you shop online or watch a video, personalized ads, auto tagging on photos, smart home devices and AI-powered customer service bots -- and that just scratches the surface.  In particular, let's look at Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) and BigBear.ai (NYSE: BBAI) as two ways to invest in the growing influence of artificial intelligence in the federal government.
